From the project folder, run the app:
     node server.js

Go to browser localhost:8080

Enter your address in the search box.

Zoom in to see your roof clearly.

Click the Create button.

Pick a corner and click.

All the action occurs in polyCreate.js.

The coordinates displayed on the screen come from positionHandler.js.

Single-clicks create the polylines (with a collection of coordinates).

Double-click will eventually create the polygon.